{"name":"Mathlib.Logic.Nonempty","instances":[{"typeNames":["Prod"],"name":"instNonemptyProd","className":"Nonempty"},{"typeNames":[],"name":"instNonemptyForAll_2","className":"Nonempty"}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Tactic.NoMatch"],"declarations":[{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L135-L136","name":"instNonemptyForAll_2","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#instNonemptyForAll_2","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L132-L133","name":"subsingleton_of_not_nonempty","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#subsingleton_of_not_nonempty","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L129-L130","name":"instNonemptyProd","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#instNonemptyProd","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L126-L127","name":"Nonempty.elim_to_inhabited","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#Nonempty.elim_to_inhabited","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L123-L124","name":"Nonempty.congr","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#Nonempty.congr","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L120-L121","name":"Nonempty.map2","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#Nonempty.map2","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L117-L118","name":"Nonempty.map","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#Nonempty.map","doc":"Given `f : α → β`, if `α` is nonempty then `β` is also nonempty.\n`Nonempty` cannot be a `functor`, because `functor` is restricted to `Type`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L112-L113","name":"Classical.arbitrary","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#Classical.arbitrary","doc":"Using `classical.choice`, extracts a term from a `Nonempty` type. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L107-L108","name":"Nonempty.some","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#Nonempty.some","doc":"Using `classical.choice`, extracts a term from a `Nonempty` type. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L102-L103","name":"Classical.inhabitedOfNonempty'","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#Classical.inhabitedOfNonempty'","doc":"Using `classical.choice`, lifts a (`Prop`-valued) `Nonempty` instance to a (`Type`-valued)\n`inhabited` instance. `classical.inhabited_of_nonempty` already exists, in\n`core/init/classical.lean`, but the assumption is not a type class argument,\nwhich makes it unsuitable for some applications. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L95-L96","name":"Classical.nonempty_pi","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#Classical.nonempty_pi","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L92-L93","name":"Nonempty.exists","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#Nonempty.exists","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L88-L89","name":"Nonempty.forall","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#Nonempty.forall","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L84-L85","name":"nonempty_plift","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#nonempty_plift","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L80-L81","name":"nonempty_ulift","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#nonempty_ulift","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L77-L77","name":"nonempty_empty","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#nonempty_empty","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L73-L74","name":"nonempty_psigma","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#nonempty_psigma","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L61-L70","name":"nonempty_psum","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#nonempty_psum","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L49-L58","name":"nonempty_sum","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#nonempty_sum","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L45-L46","name":"nonempty_pprod","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#nonempty_pprod","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.lean#L41-L42","name":"nonempty_prod","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Nonempty.html#nonempty_prod","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-comm